description: All Schwarzkopf  products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.DESCRIPTIONBlondme Bond Enforcing Premium Lightener 9+ is a high performance powder lightener. This is the first powder lightener to provide up to 9 levels of lift on natural and coloured hair. It offers perfect neutralisation thanks to it's antiyellowagents which directly target the pheomelanin in hair to avoid unwanted warm or yellow undertones. FEATURES Integrated bonding technology Up to 9 levels of lift Helps to protect the hair fiber during development for minimized hair breakage Antiyellow agents to neutralize any warm undertones Flexible mixing ratio Easy workable consistency Suitable for all techniqueHOW TO USE Always use in combination with BLONDME Premium Developers. Mix 1:1.5 to 1:2.5 (Ex: 30g BLONDME Premium Lightener 9+ and 4575 mL BLONDME Premium Developer). OnScalp Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 2% (7 Vol.) or 6% (20 Vol.). Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 9% (30 Vol.). Apply to dry hair and let develop for 20 to 45 minutes. Additional heat is not recommended. Visually check progress during development time.PROTIP For gentle lightening and optimal time control, use BLONDME Premium Developer 2% (7 Vol.). Check visually every 5 minutes.

description: All Schwarzkopf  products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.DESCRIPTIONSchwarzkopf Igora Royal Permanent colour provides total coverage and intensity while maintaining scalp comfort. Its formula allows to equalize the colour evenly even on porous hair. The pigment penetrates the hair efficiently and is locked in for longlasting, vibrant colour.FEATURES Permanent hair colour. Covers white air up to 100%. Longlasting colour retention. Intense colour vibrancy. Works even on porous hair. Absolute truetotuft results.HOW TO USE Mix the colour and developer at a ratio of 1: 1 for a normal colouring, or 1: 2 for a lighter shade. VIRGIN HAIR: apply the mixture to lengths and ends, then to roots after 15 to 20 minutes. COLOURED HAIR: apply the mixture to the regrowth, then to the lengths and tips after 15 to 30 minutes. Leave as directed on instructions. Rinse thoroughly, then wash and condition the hair.

description: All Schwarzkopf  products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.DESCRIPTIONSchwarzkopf Igora Royal Permanent colour provides total coverage and intensity while maintaining scalp comfort. Its formula allows to equalize the colour evenly even on porous hair. The pigment penetrates the hair efficiently and is locked in for longlasting, vibrant colour.FEATURES Permanent hair colour.
